name: INAG100
title: Introduction to Plant Science
description: Restriction: Must be a student in the Institute of Applied Agriculture; or permission of AGNR-Institute of Applied Agriculture department. Credit only granted for: INAG100, PLSC100, PLSC101, PLSC110 or PLSC112. A general introduction to plant science designed to provide the students with a working knowledge of the fundamental structures and processes of plants. Content includes plant anatomy, physiology, genetics and environmental relationships.
